lead_paragraph: Democrat Hillary Clinton sought to persuade African-Americans on Friday to resist any temptation to side with Republican Jeb Bush in the 2016 presidential race as they offered differing visions on how to tackle economic and racial inequality.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Takes on Jeb Bush on Racial Equality Issues
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Takes on Jeb Bush on Racial Equality Issues
